data.summary_suggestion: Batch check snapshot availability for multiple URLs
data.description_suggestion: Retrieves availability information for archived snapshots of multiple URLs in a single request. Accepts an AvailabilityRequests array containing URL specifications and optional filtering parameters (timestamp, status codes, output format, etc.). Returns AvailabilityResults containing snapshot data for each requested URL including capture dates, HTTP status codes, and archive metadata. Enables efficient bulk availability checks for multiple URLs.
